SPEAKING PRACTICE
ANSWER THE QUESTIONS. INTRODUCE YOURSELF. POST YOUR VIDEO/AUDIO IN YOUR CHAT GROUP. (ОТВЕТЬТЕ НА ВОПРОСЫ. ОПУБЛИКУЙТЕ ВИДЕО.АУДИО ПРЕДСТАВЛЕНИЯ В ЧАТЕ СВОЕЙ ГРУППЫ)
1 What's your name?  My name is Denis.
2 How old are you?  I am 26 years old.
3 Where do you live? I live in Belarus.
5 What do you like doing in your free time? I play computer games.
6 Would you like to be a programmer? Why? Yes, I would. I like programming.
7 Did you learn English before? Would you like to improve your English? What is the hardest thing about learning English? Yes, I did.  Yes, of course. There's not enough time.
